This is a small BSD server to replace the Linux hddtemp utility.

Current temperatures for all hard disks are printed on port 7634:

    MyPrompt$ nc -d localhost 7634
    |/dev/ada0|Samsung SSD 850 EVO 1TB|40|C|
    |/dev/ada1|Samsung SSD 850 EVO 1TB|40|C|

This is used by the devel/ros-diagnostic_common_diagnostics port.

WWW: https://www.guzu.net/linux/hddtemp.php
